        - Data Point: Blood pressure reduction -> Goal: Compare -> Chosen Viz: Vertical Bar Chart (Chart.js/Canvas) -> Justification: Effectively compares the two related metrics (systolic vs. diastolic) from the meta-analysis.
        - Data Point: Weight loss effect -> Goal: Inform -> Chosen Viz: Single "Big Number" stat (HTML/CSS) -> Justification: Highlights the key quantitative result from the meta-analysis in a highly scannable format.
